title: Otsuka Ai Discography [160 kbps]
description:
J-Pop
160 kbps

A collection of Otsuka Ai's studio albums (Love Punch, Love Jam, Love Cook, Love PiEce, Love Letter), sans her compilation album "Ai Am Best." Including that would just be giving you repeats of the songs.

Also included are her songs from the "Tokyo Friends: Movie Music Collection," the j-drama she starred in, as well as "Kuroge Wagyu Joshio Tan Yaki 680 Yen," which was only released as a single.

For album info, go here: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ai_Otsuka#Discography
